body.description: We provide complete customer support with our cell phone cases to ensure you have the best experience possible. With our knowledgeable team, quick response time, and friendly customer service representatives, we are always here to help make sure you have a pleasant shopping experience with us.Here are the steps for applying tempered glass to your phone: 1. Keep hands clean and dry before installation. If needed, search for the installation video on the Internet first. 2. Gently pick up the Tempered Glass from the case. 3. Predict installation position on the phone. (Align and Tag guide sticker) 4. Make sure to clean all the Dust and Fingerprints on the screen (using wet wipes, dry wipes, or dust absorbent). 5. Peel off the clear thin protective film from the screen protector back before applying on the phone. 6. Put the screen protector onto the screen horizontally and slowly. Tap the middle of the screen protector. 7. If there is a bubble, gently scrape the bubble to the edge with a card. Congratulations, With these steps, you can easily apply film to your phone and enjoy the added protection it provides！
